div.p: Major components (%) identified in the essential oil extracted from leaves of Vitex capitata, V. megapotamica, V. gardneriana and V. rufescens from northeastern Brazil a.

span.span: aThose compounds which are in bold represent the main compounds found. bRI lit., retention indices according to Adams (2007). cRI exp., retention indices on RTX-5MS column calculated according to van Den Dool and Kratz (1963). dtr = trace amounts of compound were detected. ∗co-eluting compounds.
